{"lemma":"غُمَّةٍ","slug":"غُمَّةٍ","root":"غ.م.م","root_slug":"غ-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غُمَّة","root":"غمم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32343","n32352","n32353","n32354"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8F%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the state of being grieved, sadness, mourn"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32343","headword_ar":"غَمَّهُ","root":"gm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He covered it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"veiled it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) namely, a thing: (Msb, K, TA:) this is the primary meaning. (TA.) [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gum~a AlhilaAlu","text_ar":"غُمَّ الهِلَالُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"عَلَى النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The new moon was veiled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"otherwise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was intercepted by thin clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"otherwise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it was not seen."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_ino gum~a Ealayokumo","text_ar":"فَاـِنْ غُمَّ عَلَيْكُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^akomiluwA AlEid~apa","text_ar":"فَاَكْمِلُوا العِدَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, * Msb, TA,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And if it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the new moon]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be veiled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to you, then complete ye the reckoning"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Shaabán, thirty [days], in order that the entering upon the fast of Ramadán may be with [inferential] knowledge. (Msb.) Az says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gum~a","text_ar":"غُمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ugomiYa","text_ar":"اُغْمِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gumiYa","text_ar":"غُمِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"all signify the same: (TA:) and all three occur in the trad. above mentioned accord. to different relations thereof. (Mgh.) [See also 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gmY","text_ar":"غمى"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  And [hence]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~a Alqamaru Aln~ujuwma","text_ar":"غَمَّ القَمَرُ النُّجُومَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The moon concealed the stars:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"almost concealed the light of the stars."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gum~a Ealayohi Alxabaru","text_ar":"غُمَّ عَلَيْهِ الخَبَرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The information,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narration, was dubious, confused,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vague, to him; such as to be difficult to be understood;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as not to be understood;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ugomiYa","text_ar":"اُغْمِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was obscure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unapparent, to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~ahu","text_ar":"غَمَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~","text_ar":"هَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning “ grief, ” see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covered"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was as though it covered"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his heart:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 637:) or [accord. to common acceptation]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he, grieved him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused him to mourn"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lament,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be sorrowful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sad"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unhappy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHozanahu","text_ar":"اَحْزَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, and Har p. 422. [See also 4.]) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~ahu","text_ar":"غَمَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which the pronoun relates to an ass, &c., (S, K, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to his mouth and his nostrils the"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gimaAmap","text_ar":"غِمَامَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) which is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kiEaAm","text_ar":"كِعَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"muzzle"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (so in the S and CK,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fidaAm","text_ar":"فِدَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which seems to be here similar in meaning to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kEAm","text_ar":"كعام"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (so in other copies of the K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to his mouth a nose-bag,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, to prevent his feeding;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and this is termed a ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gimaAmap","text_ar":"غِمَامَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [the verb that I have rendered “ put to ” in these explanations is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqama","text_ar":"اَلْقَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which I do not find in its proper place any signification that would be exactly apposite in this case:] or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gimaAmapN","text_ar":"غِمَامَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sort of bag for the mouth of a camel and the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his mouth being put into it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamaAy^imu","text_ar":"غَمَايِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) and one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~ahu biAlgimaAmapi","text_ar":"غَمَّهُ بِالغِمَامَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he covered his mouth with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gmAmp","text_ar":"غمامة"},{"kind":"text","text":"], aor. and inf. n. as above. (TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~a","text_ar":"غَمَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", also signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaAhu","text_ar":"عَلَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It rose upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above, the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though forming a covering over it]: mentioned on the authority of IAar, who cites [as an ex.] the saying of En-Nemir Ibn-Towlab, [app. describing a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoDap","text_ar":"رَوْضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", or meadow,]"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A^unufN yagum~u AlD~aAlu nabota biHaArihaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Not depastured, the trees called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DAl","text_ar":"ضال"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rising upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above, the herbage of its fertile tracts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its tracts near to water"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) See also 8.       -A2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~a","text_ar":"غَمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also intrans.: one says,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~a yawomunaA","text_ar":"غَمَّ يَوْمُنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gumuwmN","text_ar":"غُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agam~a","text_ar":"اَغَمَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Our day was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sultry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely hot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it took away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"almost took away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the breath:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or both verbs, said of a day, and of the sky, mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it brought"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~","text_ar":"غَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distress that affected the breath"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"respiration"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arising from closeness of heat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~a Al$~axoSu","text_ar":"غَمَّ الشَّخْصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEiba","text_ar":"تَعِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [the first pers. being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamimotu","text_ar":"غَمِمْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamamN","text_ar":"غَمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The person's hair of his head flowed down so that his forehead and the back of his neck were narrowed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamamN","text_ar":"غَمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.]"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n32352","headword_ar":"غَمَّةٌ","root":"gm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., used as an epithet."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n32353","headword_ar":"غُمَّةٌ","root":"gm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence: ―         -b2-  and also in the latter half. ―         -b3-  Also, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Perplexity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dubiousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confusedness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gumamN","text_ar":"غُمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa fiY gum~apK","text_ar":"هُوَ فِى غُمَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is in a state of perplexity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dubiousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confusedness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa fiY gum~apK mino A^amorihi","text_ar":"هُوَ فِى غُمَّةٍ مِنْ اَمْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is in a state of perplexity"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"darkness"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of his case"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algam~u","text_ar":"الغَمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ the act of covering ” [a thing]. (Ham p. 320.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gim~apN","text_ar":"غِمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~aA='u","text_ar":"غَمَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN gum~apN","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ غُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A dubious, confused,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vague, case"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K. *) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gum~aY","text_ar":"غُمَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":".] It is said in the Kur [x. 72],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~a laA yakuno A^amorukumo Ealayokumo gum~apF","text_ar":"ثُمَّ لَا يَكُنْ اَمْرُكُمْ عَلَيْكُمْ غُمَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then let not your case be to you one of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"darkness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straitness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anxiety:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, S, TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covered, veiled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN gum~apN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ غُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrow, land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bottom of the interior"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a skin for clarified butter (S, K) &c. (S.) [See also the first sentence in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gml","text_ar":"غمل"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n32354","headword_ar":"غِمَّةٌ","root":"gm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lbsp","text_ar":"لبسة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lubosapN","text_ar":"لُبْسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Obscureness, confusedness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dubiousness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gum~apN","text_ar":"غُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}